{"tid":2300802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"健康碼與  警魔昔日盜用 醫院管理局資料庫迫害警暴受害人","createTime":"2020-11-25T23:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T02:33:55.000Z","uid":26770,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4238c6ac419374b4bf098f9b76eedaa5d204e5be","tid":2300802,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:20:27.000Z","msg":"當日,香港警魔遭踢爆盜用 醫院管理局資料庫搜捕警暴受害人<br />\n狗方記招係好撚串講唔通有賊唔拉<br />\n香港法律界扮盲<br />\n私隱專員黃繼兒當見唔到,一味批評示威者起警魔底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">邊個保證警魔唔偷資料?<br />\n一係叫行政會議班畜牲保證,任何資料leak左或警魔/律政把資料呈堂就問責坐監</span>"},{"pid":"8d68db356266617e830b2d00fd21810b9b430c1e","tid":2300802,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:25:25.000Z","msg":"狗共仲有一招<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">叫黨委法官出搜查令送個server比香港警魔</span><br />\n<br />\n大把黨委法官搶住簽<br />\n法律神教班人到時一字排開屈群眾唔尊重法官都似<br />\n<br />\n搜查輪姦案受害人病歷,搜查狗屋證物房所有電話"},{"pid":"a015cf2c41270b70286b04266c4850180912ed93","tid":2300802,"uid":191588,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:29:50.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n<br />\n補充：<br />\n記者查冊就俾人拉刷，警察隨便用所有資料。<br />\n私人專員公署先唔需要扮啦，政府係豁免嘅。<br />\n<br />\n根本由制度上已經極權到極致。"},{"pid":"d3155a4e4214005c7412290043d7e4247fd6f2e3","tid":2300802,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66ca431edf542acb9f5e2cc692484a018d5647ae","tid":2300802,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230cd57fbe534162c7163454b6c53f1ad33138b2","tid":2300802,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"其實唔用 唔裝 就已經係抵抗"},{"pid":"750982bed939b812ad97b8075198dac1abd62fb1","tid":2300802,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:31:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a63a6f795e7d604ec84fec4b7aaa5ca95d560a0","tid":2300802,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d189610e205647350e53fef01de1aef1dbf26449","tid":2300802,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"私隱專員黃繼兒絕對係小人<br />\n<br />\n警魔盜用 醫院管理局資料，大量示威者係狗屋交的資料遭流出<br />\n呢條契弟從無出聲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警魔比人起底黃繼兒就立即譴責市民</strong>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d189610e205647350e53fef01de1aef1dbf26449","tid":2300802,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"私隱專員黃繼兒絕對係小人<br />\n<br />\n警魔盜用 醫院管理局資料，大量示威者係狗屋交的資料遭流出<br />\n呢條契弟從無出聲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>警魔比人起底黃繼兒就立即譴責市民</strong>"}}